{"tid":2166205,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「月入10萬不是夢」22人被騙282萬  兩男落網 同黨潛逃","createTime":"2020-08-20T09:44:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-20T10:18:17.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"cbca00c61c9ebcc82b6155b01962792f43141b16","tid":2166205,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T09:44:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200820/LFL2Q3UTJBEWVKS5MYCBHO5HIU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200820%2FLFL2Q3UTJBEWVKS5MYCBHO5HIU%2F&d=hRZI3RxrLdWDWG%2FiPctn5RVTfDkzAunSCULMKrq9Td0%3D&h=8349f7ee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200820%2FLFL2Q3UTJBEWVKS5MYCBHO5HIU%2F&h=931842b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200820/LFL2Q3UTJBEWVKS5MYCBHO5HIU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n「月入10萬不是夢」22人被騙282萬 <br />\n兩男落網 同黨潛逃<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/OboEu_HGarREWhksX9REw9oT0io=/1224x679/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MTW5M5H44FEGBC57SNET6O3SOE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FOboEu_HGarREWhksX9REw9oT0io%3D%2F1224x679%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMTW5M5H44FEGBC57SNET6O3SOE.jpg&h=19f08016&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■騙徒以「月入10萬不是夢」在網上設局誘騙。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】警方搗破一個以「月入10萬不是夢」作招徠、專門在社交媒體行騙的犯罪集團，日前拘捕兩名男騙徒，指騙徒涉嫌利用facebook及Instagram等熱門社交媒體，發放大量虛假投資帖子，吸引市民以巨款投資Bitcoin、澳門賭場，甚至申請大嶼山通行證，案中至少22名市民受騙，涉款282萬元。當中單一最大金額騙案，受害人因投資Bitcoin被騙250萬元。<br />\n<br />\n被捕兩名男騙徒，分別36歲及38歲，報稱無業，據知他們負責利用個人戶口，收取犯罪得益。警方指，該行騙集團已營運數月，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n誘買Bitcoin 申請大嶼山通行證<br />\n<br />\n警方又稱，遭搗破行騙集團主要在facebook、Instagram等熱門社交媒體上，發放虛假帖子，以吸引市民投資Bitcoin、澳門賭場。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n警方調查亦發現，騙徒又以9,800元可申請大嶼山通行證來吸引市民申請通行證，聲稱可讓申請人到大嶼山自駕遊，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n至今，騙案中共有22名市民受騙，年齡介乎16至56歲，當中包括學生及專業人士，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n■警方指不排除有更多受害人被騙。"},{"pid":"c92c7211e0471b05475ff314139ed67ed282ff68","tid":2166205,"uid":117037,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T09:49:40.000Z","msg":"又蠢又貪心比人呃除左抵撚死都唔知講乜好"},{"pid":"2755eb1f8c70b4d1ad99b783e6c319c3d8a094a5","tid":2166205,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T09:50:24.000Z","msg":"被中共委任做垃圾會議員就月入10萬啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"244282236cbf5d179e870f80c3ec165987d62ffd","tid":2166205,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T10:18:17.000Z","msg":"呃人呢班友都算係專業人仕嚟"}]}